beer.beer_description: Named in honour of our home base, the suburb of Brunswick in Melbourne, Australia. Brunswick Bitter is made with all Australian ingredients and represents a return and rethink of the long lost Australian classic bitter ale styles.  This is a sparkling ale, with zesty carbonation and distinct citrus, peach and passion fruit aroma but with a robust sessionable flavour.  Geared for sessioning.
